Thank you for checking my Clash Royale Recommendation System.

This project has the goal to help the user increase the probabilities of 
defeating his opponent in the videogame Clash Royale with special focus on the 
competitive environment.

● Using the Api of Clash Royale we obtain the most used card of the opponent and 
through a graphic interface developed with Python the system recommends 3 decks the 
user should play to beat the opponent;
● The project was tested with different players which won a total of 13 games out of
20 we tested.
